data.description: Incredible home located on over a half acre, on a quiet cul-de-sac, in  desirable Quail Canyon.  Discover the quaint, gated, courtyard entry with mature landscaping. Updated kitchen with island and patio access. 3 bedrooms PLUS an oversized space that makes perfect workshop, office or play room. Fabulous spaces for outdoor living, rear yard features full length patio, sports/basketball court and two areas that could be ideal for dog runs or gardening. Enjoy the benefits of an owned solar system. Minutes to dining, District 16 schools, shopping and the always popular Sabino Canyon!
